import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Target, Eye, MapPin, Ruler, Camera, Info } from 'lucide-react'; const BodyLandmarksGuide = () => { const [selectedLandmark, setSelectedLandmark] = useState(null); const [activeView, setActiveView] = useState('front'); // Key anatomical landmarks for upper body measurement const landmarks = { front: [ { id: 'acromion', name: 'Acromion Process', position: { x: 20, y: 25 }, description: 'Bony prominence at the outer edge of shoulder blade', measurement: 'Shoulder width (acromion to acromion)', aiDetection: 'Edge detection + shoulder contour analysis', importance: 'Critical for shirt shoulder seam placement', color: 'red' }, { id: 'suprasternal', name: 'Suprasternal Notch', position: { x: 50, y: 20 }, description: 'Hollow at the base of the throat', measurement: 'Neck circumference, torso length starting point', aiDetection: 'Facial landmark detection + neck contour', importance: 'Reference point for all vertical measurements', color: 'blue' }, { id: 'chest_point', name: 'Chest/Bust Point', position: { x: 40, y: 40 }, description: 'Fullest part of chest (nipple level for men)', measurement: 'Chest circumference', aiDetection: 'Pose estimation + body contour analysis', importance: 'Primary sizing measurement for all upper garments', color: 'green' }, { id: 'waist_front', name: 'Natural Waist', position: { x: 50, y: 60 }, description: 'Narrowest part of torso', measurement: 'Waist circumference, shirt length', aiDetection: 'Body silhouette analysis + curve detection', importance: 'Determines shirt length and fit style', color: 'purple' }, { id: 'wrist', name: 'Wrist', position: { x: 15, y: 75 }, description: 'Wrist bone prominence', measurement: 'Sleeve length', aiDetection: 'Hand/wrist pose estimation', importance: 'Sleeve length for long-sleeve garments', color: 'orange' } ], side: [ { id: 'c7_vertebra', name: 'C7 Vertebra', position: { x: 50, y: 15 }, description: 'Prominent vertebra at base of neck', measurement: 'Back neck point, shoulder slope', aiDetection: 'Neck contour + spine alignment detection', importance: 'Critical for jacket and shirt back construction', color: 'red' }, { id: 'shoulder_slope', name: 'Shoulder Slope', position: { x: 35, y: 25 }, description: 'Natural slope from neck to shoulder point', measurement: 'Shoulder angle, armhole depth', aiDetection: 'Shoulder contour analysis', importance: 'Proper armhole positioning', color: 'blue' }, { id: 'armpit', name: 'Armpit/Axilla', position: { x: 30, y: 35 }, description: 'Highest point under the arm', measurement: 'Armhole circumference, chest depth', aiDetection: 'Arm-torso junction detection', importance: 'Armhole size and chest depth measurement', color: 'green' }, { id: 'back_waist', name: 'Back Waist', position: { x: 55, y: 60 }, description: 'Natural waist from back view', measurement: 'Torso length, back waist suppression', aiDetection: 'Spine curve analysis + waist detection', importance: 'Back length and fit adjustments', color: 'purple' } ] }; // AI Detection Methods const aiMethods = [ { method: 'MediaPipe Pose', description: 'Real-time pose estimation with 33 body landmarks', accuracy: '95%+', landmarks: ['Shoulders', 'Elbows', 'Wrists', 'Hips'], use: 'Primary landmark detection' }, { method: 'OpenPose', description: 'Multi-person pose estimation', accuracy: '90%+', landmarks: ['All major joints', 'Body keypoints'], use: 'Detailed joint analysis' }, { method: 'Body Segmentation', description: 'Pixel-level body part segmentation', accuracy: '85%+', landmarks: ['Body contours', 'Circumference points'], use: 'Precise contour measurement' }, { method: 'Face Mesh + Body', description: 'Combined facial and body landmark detection', accuracy: '92%+', landmarks: ['Neck base', 'Facial reference points'], use: 'Head-neck-shoulder alignment' } ]; const measurements = [ { name: 'Chest Circumference', landmarks: ['Chest points (left & right)', 'Back chest level', 'Side armpit level'], method: 'Connect landmarks around fullest chest part', formula: 'π × (front width + back width + 2 × side depth) / 2', accuracy: '±0.5 inches' }, { name: 'Shoulder Width', landmarks: ['Left acromion', 'Right acromion'], method: 'Direct distance between shoulder points', formula: 'Euclidean distance between acromion points', accuracy: '±0.3 inches' }, { name: 'Sleeve Length', landmarks: ['Acromion', 'Elbow', 'Wrist'], method: 'Follow arm contour from shoulder to wrist', formula: 'Sum of upper arm + forearm segments', accuracy: '±0.4 inches' }, { name: 'Neck Circumference', landmarks: ['Suprasternal notch', 'C7 vertebra', 'Neck sides'], method: 'Elliptical estimation around neck base', formula: 'π × √((a² + b²)/2) where a,b are neck radii', accuracy: '±0.3 inches' }, { name: 'Torso Length', landmarks: ['C7 vertebra', 'Natural waist back'], method: 'Spine-following vertical measurement', formula: 'Curved distance along back centerline', accuracy: '±0.5 inches' } ]; return (
